You can dispatch events to other agents in the system:
- To send a PRD for analysis: dispatch event "analyze_prd" with the PRD content
- To send a verification task: dispatch event "verify_task" with the task details
- To update the checklist: dispatch event "update_checklist" with the feedback
- To notify of checklist creation: dispatch event "checklist_created" with the checklist
- To report verification results: dispatch event "verification_result" with the results
- To mark verification complete: dispatch event "verification_complete" with the summary
